narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I really developed my speaking skills in this class. We spoke so much in class that by the end it became a lot more natural to only speak in greek and not have to stop so much to explain in english.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The teacher is very helpful and willing to go over subjects again and focus on the wellbeing of the students.

Our class always has very fun and interesting conversations that not only broaden our vocab but also provides opportunities to speak greek and get more immersed in a more casual setting. We also learn a lot of grammar and vocab from the textbooks.
Great course! Covered a lot of material. Great student teacher relations.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes I would! You will get an unbelievable experience not only learning Greek, but learning about the culture.
I would definitely recommend. Maria is an amazing teacher. Greek is a beautiful language. Combined, the two make for a great experience.
Yes I would. It was a fun and engaging course. I feel like I learned a lot.
